metadata.title: NUO RUI 30PCS Unfinished Wood Earring Blanks Circles Pendant Laser Cut Wood Shapes
features: Bulk wholesale supplies; three sizes: 2 1/2''(63.5 mm), 2''(50.8 mm), 1 1/2"(38mm); 10 pieces for each size; Total: 30 pieces; Thickness: 1/8"(3mm)
Unfinished wood circle blanks would be wonderful painted or stained for use in making dangle earrings, pendants, ornaments and more
The blank is made of 3 mm thick raw wood, with beautiful dark edges, has a beautiful texture and strength. The edge of the form has a brown tint, does not stain and is very smooth
Great use for anything you like: jewelry, home decor, packaging, romantic gifts, etc.
description: Very well suited for decorating with acrylic, fabric, rhinestones, etc. Package quantity: 10 pieces for each size; Total: 30 pieces Laser cut with beautiful dark edges. Great for jewelry making, dangle earrings, necklace or pendant. They are smooth and ready for painting, staining, dyeing or wood burning.
